xtc.oop

Class CCCP

  • java.lang.Object
    • xtc.tree.Visitor
      • xtc.oop.CCCP

  • public class CCCP
extends xtc.tree.Visitor
    CCCP is a C++ printer using the visitor pattern. This file contains Visitor methods to go to each node and helper methods to handle various contextual conditions for printing nodes.
